name: Dominate in Delaware
description:
Install instructions

download both the files and make sure to have the zipped file in the same place as the .exe file. meaning if you put one in documents put the other in there as well. If that doesnt work the put the file inside the zipped filder into the place where you put the .exe file as well. To start playing the game double click the .exe file. To exit the game hit your windows or Mac key.
